Package: effectsurf
Title: Interactive 3D Estimated Marginal Surfaces for Conditional Effect
    Visualisation
Version: 0.2.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Max", "Moldovan", , "max.moldovan@adelaide.edu.au",
           role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9680-8474")),
    person("Blakely", "Paynter", , "blakely.paynter@dpird.wa.gov.au",
           role = "ctb")
    )
Description: Extends traditional 2D estimated marginal means (EMMs) into
    interactive 3D Estimated Marginal Surfaces (EMS). Provides
    model-agnostic visualisation of predictions, conditional effect sizes,
    and conditional average treatment effects (CATE) from fitted
    statistical models. Surfaces are rendered as interactive 'plotly' 3D
    charts with categorical stratification, confidence envelopes, 2D
    profile projections, and sensitivity analysis. Supports 100+ model
    classes via 'marginaleffects', with optional 'gratia' integration for
    GAM smooth surfaces.
